item.title: To God be the Glory! Great Things He Has Done
item.description: To God be the glory! Great things He has done, So loved He the world that He gave us His Son, Who yielded His life, an atonement for sin, And opened the life-gate that all may go in Praise the Lord! Praise the Lord! Let the earth hear His voice. Praise the Lord! Praise the Lord! Let the people rejoice. Oh! Come to the Father through Jesus, the Son, And give Him the glory, great things
